  "body": "Is it possible to declare a class variable in a Component class?\r\nFor example,\r\n\r\n```js\r\nclass App entends React.Component {\r\n\r\nmyVariable = true;\r\n\r\nrender(){\r\nconsole.log(this.myVariable);  //Is this possible ?\r\nreturn(\r\n// return some dom element\r\n);\r\n\r\n}\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nI used to declare such variables earlier while using client-side rendering using webpack-dev-server. But recently I moved to server-side rendering using express and webpack-middleware. Now I can not declare such class variables. \r\nWhere am I going wrong?\r\n",
